Paper: 9702011
Title: Resource Letter GPP-1: Geometric Phases in Physics
Authors: Jeeva Anandan and Joy Christian and Kazimir Wanelik
Abstract: This Resource Letter provides a guide to the literature on the geometric angles and phases in classical and quantum physics. Journal articles and books are cited for the following topics: anticipations of the geometric phase, foundational derivations and formulations, books and review articles on the subject, and theoretical and experimental elaborations and applications.
